{"tid":2018145,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［繼續今日痴線系列］手足掉煙頭同無出示身分證 黑警唔罰佢1500 而係用簡易條例告上法庭 最高判罰500 或監禁3個月","createTime":"2020-05-15T12:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T13:19:05.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3c0f6920f7af83cc57bbc9ed413f8073d76a7f7c","tid":2018145,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:23:39.000Z","msg":"一名遊行男子被指在警員面前丟棄一個煙頭，並拒絕出示身份證，事隔5個月遭控在公眾地方亂拋廢料及抗拒警員兩罪，今在九龍城法院提訊。亂拋垃圾一般處以定額罰款，但本案動用《簡易程序治罪條例》的刑事控罪，最高可判罰500元或監禁3個月。有大律師解釋，律政司可基於嚴重性決定用哪一條條例；有大律師則指除非大量或重複拋垃圾，否則刑事起訴勞師動眾，浪費公帑。<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200515/KESREK5KDCUYHVO6ZAASQOE7FE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200515%2FKESREK5KDCUYHVO6ZAASQOE7FE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexof1mNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=c52ce6df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200515%2FKESREK5KDCUYHVO6ZAASQOE7FE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=708fa4ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200515/KESREK5KDCUYHVO6ZAASQOE7FE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"dfd2550baceb1b5c110e25bbca388412471c536d","tid":2018145,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:30:48.000Z","msg":"已經算好<br />\n<br />\n遊行反政府正常告暴動"},{"pid":"0a4b07665b372db588168dd9e44fdc8165004e67","tid":2018145,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:32:38.000Z","msg":"港式法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgm